    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drowning in debt and trapped in the grind of 1990s corporate Japan, you're offered a way out: sell information on the company that signs your paycheck. As a security specialist at METTA East, you'll balance a double life—juggling office politics by day and corporate espionage by night.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Information &amp; Reputation is your currency</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day, you'll have to make small but increasingly impactful decisions while trying to balance your reputation between 4 factions: HR, Management, Security, and your Coworkers. You're reputation with different factions will make it easier (or harder) to steal information from your employer. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098910/extras/42bbc6e4c6363822ba14a763ddc797e5.poster.avif?t=1763362963\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098910/extras/42bbc6e4c6363822ba14a763ddc797e5.webm?t=1763362963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098910/extras/42bbc6e4c6363822ba14a763ddc797e5.mp4?t=1763362963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hack out of your debt</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your hacking talent to steal and sell information on your company by assembling dangerous hacks to crack secure servers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098910/extras/a8a73ed553e39879d86660410aa16a4e.poster.avif?t=1763362963\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098910/extras/a8a73ed553e39879d86660410aa16a4e.webm?t=1763362963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098910/extras/a8a73ed553e39879d86660410aa16a4e.mp4?t=1763362963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Continually upgrade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the information becomes more important, the security becomes tougher; continually upgrade your hacking ability by buying new upgrades to make more sophisticated attacks.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098910/extras/2eb48bfe331e76fa4af806252038f3ba.poster.avif?t=1763362963\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098910/extras/2eb48bfe331e76fa4af806252038f3ba.webm?t=1763362963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098910/extras/2eb48bfe331e76fa4af806252038f3ba.mp4?t=1763362963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
